          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-zunkiree-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zunkiree-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Ownership</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Every team member takes responsibility for their work</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-zunkiree-100 flex items-center justify-center">
